		<title>Mining Bitcoin for Fun and (Basically No) Profit, Part 2: The Project</title>
		<link>http://famicoman.com/2013/09/04/mining-bitcoin-for-fun-and-basically-no-profit-part-2-the-project/</link>
		<comments>http://famicoman.com/2013/09/04/mining-bitcoin-for-fun-and-basically-no-profit-part-2-the-project/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2013 22:30:28 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Famicoman</dc:creator>
